{"tid":744571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆婦女當街遭剪衣服　中國被指強迫維人放棄傳統","createTime":"2018-07-16T04:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T10:11:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e670908e957949c11e038559755f427fa043094c","tid":744571,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/photo/bkncn-20180714120141096-0714_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180714131609\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180714%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180714120141096-0714_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180714131609&h=8a96df2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有維族婦女被當街剪割衣服。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被中國政府列為恐怖組織的世界維吾爾代表大會指控，新疆當局以打擊極端宗教的名義，嚴禁維吾爾族婦女戴頭巾，並強迫維族人接受中國的傳統習俗，拒絕者遭到不同形式的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n世維會發言人迪里夏提周五（13日）向境外媒體表示，當局為強迫維族人放棄自己的信仰和傳統文化，利用行政司法等手段推行所謂的「現代生活」，例如強制剪割維族婦女的衣服，不願配合者將遭受經濟懲罰，拒絕者更會被關進再教育中心。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/bkncn-20180714120141096-0714_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180714%2Fbkncn-20180714120141096-0714_05011_001.html&d=8l4PoS5GGj2T4qBMnovWfXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=67c25ba1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/bkncn-20180714120141096-0714_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d632c30a6795def96e180555a25448872943f936","tid":744571,"uid":49588,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"土匪黨真喺痴撚線！"},{"pid":"5b0aadd06bcec953d26ab521bb7add1fa0e14d9a","tid":744571,"uid":165377,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"共產黨真係流氓政治既專家<br />\n伊斯蘭黎到中國，分分鐘連isis哈馬斯都要跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc9cb5e2f400fb053485ef4c0fa4332b40e0caf","tid":744571,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:31:24.000Z","